Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:02.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(791.649,796.952)}欢迎来到酷乐湖
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.08,0:01:04.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,﻿来酷乐湖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:04.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the goo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来到那酷乐湖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the googly-goo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.71,0:01:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你我泡进酷乐湖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me and you in the goo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爽玩厚实的糊糊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's as chunky as stew
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方正好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The perfect spot
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.31,0:01:23.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:23.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this yours?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.60,0:01:26.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:26.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几位小朋友掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You kids dropped
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.86,0:01:37.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:37.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,something
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  我去把它们丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll dispose of them
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.00,0:01:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.95,0:01:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来  包装纸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back, wrapper
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.63,0:01:58.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:58.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.59,0:02:00.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他刚说抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:00.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, he says
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.81,0:02:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My fault
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350.814,218.81)}贻贝海滩
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.65,0:02:18.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:18.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.87,0:02:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mea culpa
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.16,0:02:23.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:23.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bad
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.20,0:02:26.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请接受我最诚挚的道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:26.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please accept my sincerest apologies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,两百声哎呀后
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.96,0:02:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小包装纸  看来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, little wrapper, it looks like
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天我有得忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a busy day ahead of me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每一位居民都有义务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every citizen must do their part
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.23,0:02:58.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持海滩干净整洁无垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:58.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to keep our beaches debris-free
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾  垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trash, trash
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everywhere trash
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各种废料都捡起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Picking up flotsam and jetsam
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝是我名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's the name
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捡起垃圾我最行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And litter's my game
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你有垃圾  我就会去收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So if you got garbage I'll get some
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你有垃圾  他就会去收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So if ya got garbage he'll get some
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不能好好晒日光浴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't a guy sunbathe
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不被长矛扎屁股吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without getting a spear in the tuchus?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.55,0:03:25.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从我余光看去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:25.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From the corner of my eye
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就跟个肮脏的陈年腌椰菜似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you looked like a dirty old pickle
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万不要吃浮游生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do not eat the plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.27,0:03:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然他看着好吃  但他不是腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He may look delicious, but he is not a pickle
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是腌椰菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a pickle?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  我可是专门来这吃腌椰菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aw man, I was only here for the pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我才会特地来海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's why I even came to the beach
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是一直用这垃圾杆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I keep using this trash picker
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定得清理一整个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be here all week
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.91,0:03:48.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:48.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.33,0:03:54.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来把它设成超级吸沙模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:54.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll set it to Super-Sand-Suction
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烫到脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot foot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烫烫烫烫烫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot, hot, hot, hot, hot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码全都干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least it's all clean
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.90,0:04:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该回家去了  垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to head home, Canny
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晒得挺黑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet tans
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感应到了垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My trashy sense is tingling
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个乱扔垃圾的海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A litterbugging Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我在这里的任务还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like my job here's not done after all
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位朋友  各位农夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friends, yeomen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,country fish
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你们把垃圾给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lend me your litter
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吁  马儿慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoa, horsie
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1569.269,786.914)}裤头村\N农贸市场
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糖果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Candy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.42,0:05:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我这辈子跑得最远的一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the most I've ever run in my life
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都让一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move out of the way
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这应该会很有料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This should be delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  史赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Slappy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.11,0:05:46.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来还在期待更惨的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:46.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was hoping for much worse
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurray
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.96,0:05:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后一点也清完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the last of it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good to go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.88,0:06:03.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你造成了这么场万分愉快的车祸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:03.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for a most pleasurable traffic accident
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看多么干净啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look how clean
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.17,0:06:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷乐湖上到处一点垃圾都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a single piece of trash anywhere on Goo Lagoon
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.02,0:06:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明明把整个镇子清理干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I cleaned up this town
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.89,0:06:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我必须
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll have to
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你连同其他垃圾一起丢进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,toss you in with the rest of the rubbish
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是起风了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be windy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里一定是斜坡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I must be on a hill
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的闪避技巧是很强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your evasive moves are impressive
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But behold
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,古怪风车术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wacky Windmill-Style
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.22,0:06:56.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须得用我的独门秘技
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:56.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to use a technique that's specific to me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们海绵最熟悉的就是洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If there's one thing us sponges know, it's holes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.11,0:07:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  那可真是个好洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's a mighty fine hole
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all can come closer
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是所有人都能领略大洞之美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not everyone that can appreciate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a good-looking hole
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.66,0:07:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既要高雅又要有品味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It takes taste and sophistication
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  我后退一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll just step back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是想清理裤头村而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, all I wanted to do was clean up Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做点好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do something nice
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做一点点的善事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something b-b-beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.93,0:07:39.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:39.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I failed
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Failed
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a failure
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.32,0:07:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清洁工硬挤眼泪的老套路都能骗到你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fell for the old tears-of-a-trash-man routine
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你放进我口袋里好好保管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just put you in my pocket for safekeeping
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我口袋一定是破了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must have a hole in my pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个无情又干净的垃圾清理机器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a mean, clean, trash machine
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你  垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thank you, trash
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我此次猎捕极具挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a most challenging hunt
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及感谢你的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And for sacrificing your life
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由此我才能清理这片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I may make clean this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满是垃圾的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,littered land
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  该来刺你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, time to stab you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾跳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leapin' litter
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,游戏还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The game is still afoot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发誓过会报复海绵宝宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I swore I'd get back at SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而最好的报复方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what better way
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.20,0:08:48.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是用捡不起来的垃圾逼疯他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than driving ol' sanitation boy crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with an un-pickable piece of trash?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小屁屁还在疼着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my wittle tushy still hurts
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来爸爸这儿  垃圾宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to papa, TrashPants
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它这是在进化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's evolving?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撑住  手指头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on, fingers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're trying
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我另一瓣屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My other cheek
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.79,0:09:29.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我放手  你这捡垃圾的伪君子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:29.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off, you garbage-picking goody-goody geek
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不放手是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not lettin' go, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就来转转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's take a spin
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.81,0:09:44.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好不会再有什么意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:44.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hopefully there aren't any more surprises
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't let go
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想这么容易就摆脱我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't get rid of me that easy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.46,0:10:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我虽然倒下了  但还没出局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm down, but not out
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放手  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:29.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1497.119,849.145)}酷乐湖\N孔雀鱼高尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(360.752,796.952)}WH{\fs50.186}2{\fs72.268}O{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}电台\N悦耳金枪鱼之家\N\N自{\fnArial}2006{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}起\N专门播放追逐音乐
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.70,0:10:47.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:47.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个垃圾没油了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This piece of trash just ran out of gas
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Were you--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  一直都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was me all along
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.06,0:11:06.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:06.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who else?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乱扔垃圾的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Litterbugs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.73,0:11:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个各罚一百块
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A hundred dollar fine for the both of you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.52,0:11:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还得负责给这片海滩的垃圾都捡干净
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're picking up every piece of trash on this beach
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直捡到年底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the rest of the year
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.66,0:11:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又害得我们碰上烂摊子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is another fine mess you've gotten us into
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:37.71,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFC1&}蟹堡食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(751.566,409.517)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(769.603,702.602)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:43.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
