Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(290.605,387.435)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.39,0:11:56.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整理账单可太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:56.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Filing bills is so boring
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于有点正事做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, a little action
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是蟹堡王  蟹黄堡之家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've reached the Krusty Krab, home of the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是店长蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, proprietor, speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍女儿好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hiya, Pearly-girl
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个天大的好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have wonderful news
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,学校里的食堂大妈  莱诺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The school lunch lady, Lenore
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今早掉进工业用蛋糕搅拌机里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fell into the industrial cake mixer this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在伤得可重了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now she's horribly injured
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那还
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.26,0:12:22.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算好消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:22.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wonderful?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我跟大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because I told everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会来做蟹黄堡给大家当午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you would come and serve Krabby Patties for lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我就会是全校最酷的女生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm the coolest girl in school
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  你要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不怎么喜欢自己当年的高中经历
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't exactly love me last go-around in high school
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(681.42,475.762)}参与奖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1497.119,937.472)}尤金蟹\N羽毛球初级校队
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.62,0:12:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托了  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Daddy, please
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想你能引来多少新客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think of all the new customers you could make
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,New customers?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就喜欢早早树立品牌忠诚度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like building brand loyalty early
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll do it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yippee
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快一点  午餐时间要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And hurry up, it's almost lunchtime
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.81,0:13:15.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:15.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带上锅铲  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab your spatul-er, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要回高中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're headin' back to high school
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去掌管食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to man the cafeteri-er
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.07,0:13:27.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道我曾经的音乐老师还在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:27.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if my old music teacher is still there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以突然出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could pop in
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.45,0:13:32.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给小朋友们启发一点音乐灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:32.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and give the kids a little musical inspiration
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是别跟过来了  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not comin' with, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要有人留在这掌舵看店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need someone manning the helm here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's roll, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看管好蟹堡王的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on things
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be back soon
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少今天没什么生意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least it's a slow day
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来睡个美容觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to get some beauty rest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1152.401,479.777)}高中
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是母校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ol' alma mater
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝绝对对无一例外最后重申
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Absolutely, without exception, and for the final time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.41,0:14:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡独轮车严禁入校园
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bubble unicycles are strictly
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,prohibited on school grounds"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是新规定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That must be new
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad you're here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往那边走就是食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cafeteria's that way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(785.637,134.498)}食堂
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我酷一把
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for making me cool
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.24,0:14:52.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里比想象中还要有点压抑  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:52.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is slightly more grim than expected, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起来  你们这些懒鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get up, you lazy flounders
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没排好队就不准吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one eats until you form an orderly line
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the rules
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁插队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's cuttin' in my line?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是新来的食堂员工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're the new kitchen crew
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定就是食堂大妈莱诺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you must be Lunch Lady Lenore
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到你还在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't think you'd be here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.18,0:15:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我掌管这家食堂已经40年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've run this cafeteria for 40 years
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.22,0:15:20.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以为我被搅拌机弄残废就不干了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think I'm gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let a little horrific mangling keep me away?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回岗位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get to your stations
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.02,0:15:23.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:23.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  开始做蟹黄堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, time to get cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.17,0:15:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在做准备  要煎肉饼做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting ready to grill up some Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的食堂严禁外带食物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No outside food in my cafeteria
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只许吃批准入内的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Approved foods only
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the rules
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不想违反规定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd hate to be a rule-breaker
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看小朋友们今天都吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see what the kids are gettin' today
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(591.232,409.517)}菜单
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煮海带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boiled kelp?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煮肉糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boiled loaf?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.65,0:16:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煮蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boiled cake?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds awful
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过要是我肉糕做得够好吃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Although, if I make the meatloaf tasty enough
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,食物用不着你来做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't cook the food
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.91,0:16:24.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,食品仓库早都预制好料理包送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's delivered in boiling bags
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the food depository
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去煮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get to boiling
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, old man
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍答应过我们有蟹黄堡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl promised us Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家先冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的随时都会送到大家手上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be getting served any minute now
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我的厨子送上你们的蟹黄堡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as soon as me cook delivers up yer Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, hurry up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.31,0:16:48.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:48.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this, boy-o?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船上禁闭室里的食物卖相都比这好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've seen tastier lookin' meals in the brig
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的蟹黄堡哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's all my Krabby Patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the rules
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feed me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That isn't a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太没味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So flavorless
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我不能就这样子工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I can't work like this
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没调料的食物违背了煎炸厨师的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unseasoned food goes against the fry cook's code
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.02,0:17:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好我带来了自己私藏的香辛料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing I brought my secret stash
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of herbs and spices
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.91,0:17:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这般美味  就好像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The deliciousness is, like
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在激起我年轻的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stimulating my young mind
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.01,0:17:59.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,风味会害小孩子无法无天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:59.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flavor causes unruly children
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以得禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is forbidden
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回去煮料理包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now back to boiling bags
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.93,0:18:04.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:04.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去丢垃圾给小孩子吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to slinging slop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准激励小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no inspiring the children
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the rules
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我爸的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my dad's Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是全裤头村最美味的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are the tastiest food in town
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.03,0:18:19.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定会是最棒的午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:19.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be the best lunch ever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  这是在开玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, is this some kind of a joke?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么没给大家做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you serving Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明明都答应过大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like I promised everyone?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只能做这坨垃圾给大家吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't serve nothin' but this slop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个食堂大妈盯得可紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while that lunch lady is watchin'
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想吃蟹黄堡  就得引开她注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want patties, we need a distraction
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既能让她入迷  又微妙到不易察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something engrossing, but, you know, subtle
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最大的特点就是微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Subtle is my middle name
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目光朝我这边放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep on looking straight at me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用看别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else you need to see
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.94,0:18:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这又是干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's all this now?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.94,0:19:02.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,引开你的注意力  万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:02.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,D-I-S, T-R-A, C-T-I-O-N, hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, boy-o, now's our chance
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快利用这些小孩子树立品牌忠诚度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to build some brand loyalty with these brats
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上蟹黄堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring on the patties
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后边又是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on out there?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pay me attention
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外带食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Outside food?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快乐的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy children?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.24,0:19:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,违反规定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's against the rules
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme those patties
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think so
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的人气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My popularity
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨这坨垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate this slop
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,食物大战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food fight?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种事违反规定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's against the rules
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份食堂大妈特餐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One lunch lady special
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都违反了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all breaking the--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.86,0:21:02.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做了这么多年的学校食堂午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:02.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All those years of cooking school lunches
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.57,0:21:06.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都忘了风味竟能有如此之乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:06.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,made me forget how fun flavor can be
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank ya, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.41,0:21:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是在尽煎炸厨师的责任  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just doing a fry cook's duty, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up, children
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家上校车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone on the buses
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.00,0:21:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去蟹堡王做校外教学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're taking a field trip to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.38,0:21:25.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,食堂大妈能组织校外教学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:25.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can a lunch lady do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.93,0:21:26.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:26.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.14,0:21:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的噩梦总算结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, my nightmare is over
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,食物大战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food fight
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.05,0:22:05.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这也太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:05.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This rules
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要我干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.59,0:22:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都不用干  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a thing, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们丢得越多  就买得越多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The more they throw, the more they buy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.97,0:22:15.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进厨房里去  多做点弹药出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:15.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get in that kitchen and grill up more ammunition
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.23,0:22:16.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:16.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弹药来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Incoming
